                </div>
                <br>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-sm-4">
                        <div class="affi-wrap">
                            <div class="affi-icon">
                                <i class="fas fa-user-plus"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div class="affi-title">
                                <h2>Sign Up</h2>
                            </div>
                            <div class="affi-desc">
                                <p>In the first step you need to sign up</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-sm-4">
                        <div class="affi-wrap">
                            <div class="affi-icon">
                                <i class="fas fa-share"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div class="affi-title">
                                <h2>Promote Our Services</h2>
                            </div>
                            <div class="affi-desc">
                                <p>You can try to recommend our services to a friend or colleague</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-sm-4">
                        <div class="affi-wrap">
                            <div class="affi-icon">
                                <i class="fas fa-wallet"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div class="affi-title">
                                <h2>Get Paid</h2>
                            </div>
                            <div class="affi-desc">
                                <p>You will get Commission rate on your friend's money spent, as if your friend did a $ 100 business with us, Commission rate will be given to you.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm-12">
            
                    <div class="well">
                        <div class="table-responsive">
